HEADWORD: Stelled
<hw>Stelled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Stell</er> to
place.]</ety> <def>Firmly placed or fixed.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧The <xex>stelled</xex> fires⟦rdquo⟧ [the stars]. <au>Shak.</au>
<note>[In this passage by some defined as ⟦ldquo⟧starry,⟦rdquo⟧ as if
from <xex>stellatus</xex>.]</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

